    {"question": "What are planetary aspects?", "answer": "Planetary aspects are angles formed between planets in a chart that describe how the planets interact with each other."},
    {"question": "What is Mercury retrograde?", "answer": "Mercury retrograde is when the planet Mercury appears to move backward in the sky, often associated with communication issues, delays, and technological glitches."},
    {"question": "What is Venus retrograde?", "answer": "Venus retrograde occurs every 18 months and affects love, relationships, finances, and personal values."},
    {"question": "What is Mars retrograde?", "answer": "Mars retrograde happens approximately every two years and can affect energy levels, motivation, and physical activity."},
    {"question": "What are the 12 houses in astrology?", "answer": "The 12 astrological houses represent different areas of life such as self, money, communication, home, creativity, health, relationships, transformation, travel, career, friendships, and spirituality."},
    {"question": "What is the first house?", "answer": "The first house governs self-image, the body, and how you present yourself to the world."},
    {"question": "What is the second house?", "answer": "The second house relates to personal finances, possessions, and values."},
    {"question": "What is the third house?", "answer": "The third house governs communication, siblings, short trips, and early education."},
    {"question": "What is the fourth house?", "answer": "The fourth house is associated with home, family, roots, and emotional foundations."},
    {"question": "What is the fifth house?", "answer": "The fifth house rules creativity, romance, children, and self-expression."},
    {"question": "What is the sixth house?", "answer": "The sixth house deals with health, daily routines, work, and service to others."},
    {"question": "What is the seventh house?", "answer": "The seventh house is about partnerships, marriage, and one-on-one relationships."},
    {"question": "What is the eighth house?", "answer": "The eighth house governs shared resources, intimacy, death, rebirth, and transformation."},
